Introduction

Rainbow is a seven-member South Korean girl group under DSP Media. The group consists of Jaekyung, Woori, Seungah, Noeul, Yoonhye, Jisook, and Hyunyoung. Rainbow officially debuted on November 14, 2009. In November 2019, the group reunited for their 10th anniversary celebration and released the single 'Aurora'.
